<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="description" content="MP3Juice is a free MP3 search engine with a built-in downloader. Find and download your favorite music from YouTube and SoundCloud — no sign-up required."><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>MP3Juice - Free MP3 Downloader - MP3 Juice</title><link rel="canonical" href="https://mp3juice.sc/"><style>body{background-color:#2a2d31;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;margin:0;}input, button{font-family:inherit;}.header{text-align:center;max-width:600px;border-bottom:1px solid #3d4147;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 0;}.header a{color:#ebecee;text-decoration:none;margin:0 6px;}.logo{text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:32px auto 0 auto;}form{background-color:#353940;max-width:600px;border:1px solid #4d525a;border-radius:8px;margin:32px auto 0 auto;padding:6px;box-sizing:border-box;}.form{display:flex;gap:12px;}.form__input{flex:1;position:relative;}.form__action{position:relative;}form input, form button{font-size:16px;height:48px;border:none;border-radius:6px;margin:0;}form input{color:#ebecee;background-color:transparent;width:100%;padding:0 12px;box-sizing:border-box;outline:none;}form button{color:#0a2540;background-color:#7eb3ff;font-weight:normal;padding:0 24px;cursor:pointer;}form .form__processing{background-color:#7eb3ff;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;}form .suggestions{background-color:#353940;list-style-type:none;width:100%;border:1px solid #4d525a;border-top:none;border-bottom-right-radius:8px;border-bottom-left-radius:8px;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:54px;left:-7px;}form .suggestions li{color:#ebecee;font-size:16px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;padding:6px 18px;cursor:pointer;}form .suggestions li:hover, form .suggestions li.active{background-color:#424751;}form .suggestions li:last-child{border-bottom-right-radius:12px;border-bottom-left-radius:12px;padding-bottom:12px;}.form__loader{width:16px;height:16px;border:2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-top-color:#ffffff;border-radius:50%;box-sizing:border-box;animation:spin 0.8s linear infinite;}@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}form + div{color:#ebecee;font-size:12px;text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:12px auto 0 auto;}form + div a{color:#ebecee;}.text{color:#c8ccd2;max-width:600px;margin:48px auto 0 auto;}.text h1{color:#ebecee;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;line-height:24px;margin:0;}.text p{line-height:24px;margin:16px 0 0 0;}.text ol{list-style-position:inside;padding:0;margin:16px 0 0 0;}.text li{line-height:24px;margin-bottom:16px;}.text li:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}.text a{color:#ebecee;}.footer{text-align:center;max-width:600px;border-top:1px #3d4147 solid;margin:48px auto 0 auto;padding:24px 0;}.footer a{color:#ebecee;font-size:12px;text-decoration:none;margin:0 6px;}@media only screen and (max-width:600px) {.header{margin:0 4%;}.header a:nth-of-type(3){display:none;}form{margin:32px 4% 0 4%;}.text{margin:48px 4% 0 4%;}.footer{margin:48px 4% 0 4%;}}</style></head><body><div class="header"><a href="/">Home</a><a href="/faq/">FAQ</a><a href="/add-on/">Add-On</a><a href="/bookmarklet/">Bookmarklet</a></div><div class="logo"><img src="/svg/1781433573/logo.svg" width="189" height="74" alt="MP3Juice"></div><form autocomplete="off" method="post"><div class="form"><div class="form__input"><input id="query" type="text" name="query" aria-label="Search MP3Juice" placeholder="Search MP3Juice" inputmode="search" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" autofocus required></div><div class="form__action"><button type="submit">Search</button></div></div></form><div>By pressing &ldquo;Search&rdquo; you confirm your consent to our <a href="/terms-of-use/" target="_blank">Terms of Use</a>. </div><div class="text"><h1>MP3Juice Downloader</h1><p>MP3Juice is a free MP3 search engine with a built-in downloader that lets you find and save music from YouTube and SoundCloud. No sign-up, no subscription, no app installation required — everything runs directly in your browser. It works seamlessly on computers, tablets, and mobile phones. By using our service, you agree to our <a href="/terms-of-use/">Terms of Use</a>.</p><p>How do I use MP3Juice?</p><ol><li>Enter your search query in the field above. Suggestions may appear to help you find the exact match. Click the &ldquo;Search&rdquo; button to continue. You can also paste a YouTube link directly into the search field to get the track as an instant result.</li><li>MP3Juice will then search YouTube for matching results. Once matching tracks appear, you'll see a list that can be downloaded as MP3 or MP4 files. YouTube downloads are available in 192 kbps audio quality. You can also listen to any result by clicking the &ldquo;Play&rdquo; button.</li><li>If you'd like more options, extend your search to SoundCloud by clicking the &ldquo;Load SoundCloud results&rdquo; button at the end of the list. Please note that SoundCloud results can only be downloaded as MP3 files in 128 kbps.</li><li>Choose your favorite result and click the &ldquo;Download&rdquo; button. SoundCloud tracks download instantly, while YouTube results need to be converted into the final format first. This may take a moment. Once the conversion is complete, click the &ldquo;Download&rdquo; button to save your file. Thank you for using MP3Juice.</li></ol><p>Thank you for using MP3Juice.</p></div><div class="footer"><a href="/contact/">Contact</a><a href="/copyright-claims/">Copyright Claims</a><a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a><a href="/sra/">SRA</a><a href="/terms-of-use/">ToU</a></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebSite","name":"MP3Juice","alternateName":["MP3 Juice","MP3Juices","MP3 Juices","MP3 Download","MP3 Downloader","mp3juice.sc"],"url":"https://mp3juice.sc/"}</script><script src="/js/1781433573/mp3juice.js" defer></script></body></html>